data.name: textBoxDescription.Text
data.value:
Purpose of this program is providing a dynamic interface for managing the server in all aspects. It will ease most of management issues and save lots of precious time. In order to use this program, either the integrated SMI shoud be activated on the server side, or the module(plug-in) should be installed and activated.
The client uses DevExpress for interface design, and Resharper for code structuring.
